strings: <voice_0x01000E8F><se_def>Prince Charmles: I simply cannot fathom why Father won't just accept my decision and stop trying to force me to undergo that ridiculous initiation!

<voice_0x01000E90><se_def>Prince Charmles: It's absurd to expect me to go to the royal
hunting ground all on my own and defeat
a lizard!
<voice_0x01000E91><se_def>Prince Charmles: Urgh... A lizard! The name alone is enough to give me the willies! The world would be a much better place without them in my opinion.
<voice_0x01000E92><se_def>Prince Charmles: I saw a portrait of Princess Medea and she looked like an absolute peach! I'd marry her tomorrow if I could.
<voice_0x01000E93><se_def>Prince Charmles: But first I have to get this tedious initiation out of the way...
<voice_0x01000E94><se_def>Prince Charmles: Oh! I can't do it! I just can't do it! At this rate, I'll never be able to marry Princess Medea...
<voice_0x01000E95><se_def>Prince Charmles: Blast and botheration! Why did I have the misfortune to be born a prince!?

<voice_0x01000E96><se_def>Prince Charmles: If only I were a lowly commoner, I wouldn't have to worry about this silly initiation!
Oh, I just can't abide those awful lizards!
<voice_0x01000E97><se_def>Prince Charmles: But if I were a lowly commoner, I don't suppose I should ever be able to marry a rare beauty like Princess Medea... Oh, life is so cruel!
<voice_0x01000E99><se_def>Prince Charmles: Is there something on my head?

<voice_0x01000E9C><se_def>Prince Charmles: Ick! Ick! A lizard! What's it doing here?
Get it out! Get it out!
